{"label":"Algebraic Expressions and Operations (NIOS - level c)","id":"algebra-expressions-nios","lockAfter":100,"list":[{"label":"Number of Terms","id":"no-of-terms","type":"classifySentence","commonData":{"title":"Identify the number of terms in the below expression.","fontSize":"1.5rem","fracFontSize":"1.2rem","textAlign":"center","variableOptions":true},"data":["~-7ūĚĎ• | 1, 0, 2\n2/f + q | 2, 1, 3\n~3ūĚĎ•2-ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß+6 | 3, 2, 1\n4t + 1/2 ~ft2 | 2, 3, 4\n~abc+2fgh-af2-bg2-ch2 | 5, 4, 3","3t | 1, 0, 2\n~ūĚĎ•2+3ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ | 2, 1, 3\n~t2+3t + 1/~t2 | 3, 2, 4, 5\n~a3-b3+3 | 3, 2, 4, 5\nab+bc-ca | 3, 2, 1, 5\n~ūĚĎ•2+ūĚĎ¶2+ūĚĎß2-2hūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ |  4, 2, 3"]},{"type":"numberInput","id":"find-coeff","label":"Find the co-efficient","data":{"title":"Find the co-efficient","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":[{"text":"Find the co-efficient of t in the term 't'?\nAns = ?0\n1","vars":"rst"},{"text":"Find the co-efficient of m in the term\n2/3 ~m2n2 ?\nAns = ?0\n2mn2/3","vars":"kmn"},"Find the co-efficient of ~ūĚĎ•2 in the term\n~-25ūĚĎ•3ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß ?\nAns = ?0\n-25ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß","Find the co-efficient of ~ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß in the term\n~-25ūĚĎ•3ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß ?\nAns = ?0\n-25ūĚĎ•3","Find the co-efficient of ~5ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß in the term\n~-25ūĚĎ•3ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß ?\nAns = ?0\n-5ūĚĎ•2",{"text":"Find the co-efficient of ~a2 in the term ~a2ūĚĎ¶2ūĚĎß ?\nAns = ?0\nūĚĎ¶2ūĚĎß","vars":"aūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß"},{"text":"Find the co-efficient of st in the term ~3s3t3/7 ?\nAns = ?0\n3s2t2/7","vars":"rst"},{"text":"Find the co-efficient of 5t in the term ~-15qr2t2 ?\nAns = ?0\n-3qr2t","vars":"qrst"},{"text":"Find the co-efficient of ~ūĚĎ•3ūĚĎ¶2 in the term ~7ūĚĎ•5ūĚĎ¶3ūĚĎß2 ?\nAns = ?0\n7ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß2","vars":"ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß"}]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"numerical-factors","label":"Numerical factors","data":{"title":"Find the numerical factors in the below expression.","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":["~3ūĚĎ¶2/~ūĚĎ•2 + 5\nAns = ?0 and ?1\n3, 5","5/ūĚĎ• - 3\nAns = ?0 and ?1\n5, -3",{"text":"~2a2b - 1/7\nAns = ?0 and ?1\n2, -1/7","vars":"abc"},{"text":"~-3st3/7 - 5/7\nAns = ?0 and ?1\n-3/7, -5/7","vars":"rst"}]}},{"id":"classify-like-unlike","label":"Like vs Unlike Terms","type":"classifySentence","data":{"title":"Classify the below pairs as like and unlike terms.","fracFontSize":"1.5rem","fontSize":"2rem","textAlign":"center","types":[{"name":"Like Terms","text":"ūĚĎ•/ūĚĎ¶ , -7ūĚĎ•/ūĚĎ¶ , ūĚĎ•/7ūĚĎ¶\n~a2b2c2 , ~-b2c2a2"},{"name":"Unlike Terms","text":"1 , t\nūĚĎ• , ūĚĎ¶ \n1/3 ~ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶ , ~-ūĚĎ¶2ūĚĎ• , 5ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶"}]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"simplify","label":"Simplify","data":{"title":"Simplify the expression by merging the like terms.","fontSize":"1.5rem","fracFontSize":"1.3rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":["~ūĚĎ•2-ūĚĎ¶2+3ūĚĎ•2-4ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶\nAns = ?0\n4ūĚĎ•2-ūĚĎ¶2-4ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶","~5ūĚĎ•-3ūĚĎ¶+ 3ūĚĎ•/5 +5\nAns = ?0\n28ūĚĎ•/5-3ūĚĎ¶+5","~ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß-ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎßūĚĎ•+ūĚĎßūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶+ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß\nAns = ?0\nūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß+ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß","ūĚĎ• + 1/ūĚĎ• + 1/7 ūĚĎ• - 1/ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶\nAns = ?0\n8ūĚĎ•/7+1/ūĚĎ•-1/ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶",{"text":"~a2ūĚĎ¶2-2a2ūĚĎ¶2+ūĚĎ¶- 7/ūĚĎ¶\nAns = ?0\n-a2ūĚĎ¶2+ūĚĎ¶-7/ūĚĎ¶","vars":"aūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶"},{"text":"~5mn-3m3n3+5m2n2 + 1/2 mn\nAns = ?0\n11mn/2-3m3n3+5m2n2","vars":"kmn"},"7ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶+3ūĚĎ•\nAns = ?0\n10ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶","~2[ūĚĎ•+5(ūĚĎ•+2)]-6\n= 2[ ?0 + ?1 ] - 6\n= ?2\n6ūĚĎ•, 10, 12ūĚĎ•+14","( ~2ūĚĎ•3+7ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶2+9ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶3 )\n+ ( ~6+ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶2-3ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶3 )\nAns = ?0\n2ūĚĎ•3+8ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶2+6ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶3+6 | 8ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶2+6ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶3+2ūĚĎ•3+6","~2[4ūĚĎ•+3{2+(ūĚĎ•+1)} + ūĚĎ•]\n= 2[4ūĚĎ•+ ?0 + ?1 + ūĚĎ•]\n= 2[ ?2 + ?3 ]\n= ?4\n3ūĚĎ•, 9, 8ūĚĎ•, 9, 16ūĚĎ•+18","~ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß2-(7ūĚĎ•-2ūĚĎ¶)-10ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß2\nAns = ?0\n-7ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶-9ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß2 | -9ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß2-7ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶","~7-2[4ūĚĎ•-(1-3ūĚĎ•)]\n= 7 - 2[ ?0 ]\n= 7 - ?1\n= ?2\n7ūĚĎ•-1, 14ūĚĎ•-2, -14ūĚĎ•+9|9-14ūĚĎ• ","-2(3ūĚĎ•-ūĚĎß)-(ūĚĎß-ūĚĎ¶)+5(ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶)\n= ?0 -(ūĚĎß-ūĚĎ¶) + ?1\n= ?2\n-6ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎß, 5ūĚĎ•+10ūĚĎ¶, -ūĚĎ•+11ūĚĎ¶+ūĚĎß","(ūĚĎ•-1)(ūĚĎ•+1)(ūĚĎ•-2)(ūĚĎ•+2)\nWe know (ūĚĎ•-a)(ūĚĎ•+a) = ~ūĚĎ•2-a2\n= ( ~ūĚĎ•2-1 ) √ó ( ?0 )\n= ~ūĚĎ•2 ( ??0 ) -1 ( ??0 )\n= ?1 + ?2\n= ?3\nūĚĎ•2-4, ūĚĎ•4-4ūĚĎ•2, -ūĚĎ•2+4, ūĚĎ•4-5ūĚĎ•2+4"]}},{"id":"classify-poly","label":"Classify Polynomial","type":"classifySentence","commonData":{"title":"Classify the Algebraic Expression","fracFontSize":"1.5rem","fontSize":"2rem","textAlign":"center","types":["Monomial","Binomial","Trinomial"]},"data":[["~-7ūĚĎ•3ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß\n-1","3t+ 2/5 ~st2\n~3ūĚĎ•2-5\np+q\n~u2v+9v3\n~a3-9b3\n~3t2p+5\n~4ūĚĎ•4ūĚĎ¶3+3ūĚĎß5","~at2+2hst+bs2\n~a2+2ab+b2\n~a3-b3-2abc\n~3p-qr+s\n~m2+m+2\n~ūĚĎ•2+ūĚĎ¶2-ūĚĎß2"],["0","~3ūĚĎß+7\n~p-3q","~t2-5t+2\n~ūĚĎ•3-3ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶+ūĚĎ¶3"]]},{"type":"numberInput","id":"find-degree","label":"Find the Degree","data":{"title":"Find the Degree of the below algebraic expression","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","list":[" ~4ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶\nAns = ?0\n3"," ~2ūĚĎ•2\nAns = ?0\n2"," 8\nAns = ?0\n1"," ~3ūĚĎ•2ūĚĎ¶+7ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶-5ūĚĎ•+6\nAns = ?0\n3"]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"find-value","label":"Find the Value","data":{"title":"Find the value of the below algebraic expression","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"list":["For ūĚĎ• = 1, ūĚĎ¶ = -1, find the value of\n~ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎ•2-{1}/{3}~ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶2+3\n= ?0 + ?1/?2 + ?3\n= ?4/?5\n-1, -1, 3, 3, 5, 3","For ūĚĎ¶ = 0, ūĚĎß = -1, find the value of\n~5ūĚĎ¶-ūĚĎß\nAns = ?0\n1","For ūĚĎ•=2, ūĚĎ¶=-1 and ūĚĎß=-2, find the value of \n-ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶+ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß+ūĚĎßūĚĎ•\n= ?0 + ?1 + ?2\n= ?3\n2, 2, -4, 0","For a= 1 and b= 2, find the value of \n2a/b\n= ?0/?1\n= ?2\n2, 2, 1","For a=3 and b=2, find the value of \n(a+b)(a-b)\n= ?0 √ó ?1\n= ?2\n5, 1, 5","For ūĚĎ•=3, ūĚĎ¶=-1 and ūĚĎß=-3, find the value of\nūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎß+ūĚĎ¶ūĚĎßūĚĎ•+ūĚĎßūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶\n= ?0 + ?1 + ?2\n= ?3\n9, 9, 9, 27","For ūĚĎ•=-1, ūĚĎ¶=-1 and ūĚĎß=2, find the value of\n~2ūĚĎ•3ūĚĎ¶-3ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶2+ūĚĎß\n= ?0 + ?1 + ?2\n= ?3\n2, 3, 2, 7","For a=b=c=d=2, find the value of \n~a2+b2+c2-3d2\n= ?0 + ?1 + ?2 + ?3\n= ?4\n4, 4, 4, -12, 0","For ūĚĎ•=5 and ūĚĎ¶=12, find the value of \n~ūĚĎ•2+ūĚĎ¶2-169\n= ?0 + ?1 - 169\n= ?2 - 169\n= ?3\n25, 144, 169, 0","For s=5 and t=3, find the value of \n~(s+t)(s-t)\n= ?0 √ó ?1\n= ?2\n8, 2, 16"]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"add","label":"Addition","data":{"title":"Add the following expressions","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":[{"text":"4a+3b‚Äď12c \n2a-5c\nAns = ?0\n6a+3b-17c","vars":"abc"},{"text":"7-14ūĚĎ•\n5ūĚĎ•-a-3\nAns = ?0\n4-9ūĚĎ•-a | -9ūĚĎ•-a+4 | -9ūĚĎ•+4-a","vars":"ūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶a"},{"text":"4a+3b-12c\nb+2c\n6a-c\nAns = ?0\n10a+4b-11c","vars":"abc"}]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"sub","label":"Subtraction","data":{"title":"Subtract the second expression from the first.","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":["7ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶\n3ūĚĎ•\nAns = ?0\n4ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶",{"text":"4a+3b‚Äď12c \n2a-5c\nAns = ?0\n2a+3b-7c","vars":"abc"}]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"mul","label":"Multiply Algebraic Expression","data":{"title":"Multiplication","fontSize":"1.2rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":[{"text":"Multiply (s+2) by 5\nAns = ?0\n5s+10","vars":"stu"},"Multiply 2ūĚĎ• and ~ūĚĎ•2-2ūĚĎ•+1\nAns = ?0\n2ūĚĎ•3-4ūĚĎ•2+2ūĚĎ•","Multiply 2ūĚĎ•+5 and 2ūĚĎ•+3\nAns = 2ūĚĎ•(2ūĚĎ•+3) + 5(2ūĚĎ•+3)\n= ?0 + ?1\n= ?2\n4ūĚĎ•2+6ūĚĎ•, 10ūĚĎ•+15, 4ūĚĎ•2+16ūĚĎ•+15","ūĚĎ¶ ( ~3ūĚĎ¶2+5ūĚĎ¶-6 )\nAns = ?0 \n3ūĚĎ¶3+5ūĚĎ¶2-6ūĚĎ¶",{"text":"( ~a2-b2 )ab\nAns = ?0 \na3b-ab3","vars":"abc"}]}},{"type":"numberInput","id":"stmt-prog","label":"Write the Statements","data":{"title":"Convert the statements into expression.","fontSize":"1rem","fracFontSize":"1rem","isSentence":true,"algebra":true,"list":["Lets take a number ūĚĎ•.\nMultiply it by 2 : ?0\nAdd the double of the second number (ūĚĎ¶): ?1\nSubtract 4 : ?2\nDivide by 2 : ?3\nSubtract ūĚĎ¶ : ?4\nAdd 2 : ?5\n2ūĚĎ•, 2ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶, 2ūĚĎ•+2ūĚĎ¶-4, ūĚĎ•+ūĚĎ¶-2, ūĚĎ•-2, ūĚĎ•","Think of a number ūĚĎ•.\nMultiply it by 3 : ?0\nIn it add a number which is 1 more than the original number : ?1\nAdd 7 to it : ?2\nDivide by 4 : ?3\nSubtract 2 : ?4\n3ūĚĎ•, 4ūĚĎ•+1, 4ūĚĎ•+8, ūĚĎ•+2, ūĚĎ•"]}},{"id":"classify-poly-2","label":"Classify Polynomials","type":"classifySentence","data":{"title":"Classify the Polynomials","fracFontSize":"1.5rem","fontSize":"2rem","textAlign":"center","types":[{"name":"Monomial","text":"0"},{"name":"Binomial","text":"~ut + 1/2 ~gt2\n~v2-u2"},{"name":"Trinomial","text":"~ūĚĎ•2+ūĚĎ¶2-a2\n~aūĚĎ•2+2hūĚĎ•ūĚĎ¶+būĚĎ¶2\n~p2+2pq+q2"}]}}]}